174
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na ono dječje.

175
00:13:57,000 --> 00:14:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Očekivajući da će nas neko sad spasiti.

176
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Neki odrasli sad će nas spasiti.

177
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo imamo sve u sebi.

178
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo sve u sebi.

179
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:07,000
